---
import Layout from '../../layouts/bitcoin-tutorial/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Interactive Bitcoin Education Series">
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Interactive Bitcoin Education Series</h1>
		<p class="text-xl mb-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">A progressive educational journey from basic money concepts to Bitcoin's revolutionary potential.</p>
		
		<div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:shadow-gray-900/20 p-6 mb-8 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Series Overview</h2>
			<p class="mb-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
				Welcome to our interactive educational series on Bitcoin and monetary systems. This series is designed to take you on a journey from understanding the basic concepts of money to exploring Bitcoin's potential to revolutionize our financial system.
			</p>
			<p class="mb-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
				Each module contains interactive visualizations and simulations to help you understand complex concepts in an engaging way. Complete the quizzes at the end of each module to track your progress.
			</p>
			
			<div class="mt-6">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">How to Use This Series</h3>
				<ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 pl-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
					<li>Navigate through modules using the sidebar on the left</li>
					<li>Interact with visualizations to explore concepts</li>
					<li>Complete the quiz at the end of each module</li>
					<li>Your progress will be saved automatically</li>
				</ol>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
			<a href="/bitcoin-tutorial/module/1" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:shadow-gray-900/20 p-6 hover:shadow-lg dark:hover:shadow-gray-900/30 transition-all duration-200 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-600 group">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 group-hover:text-primary-600 dark:group-hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">Module 1: What is Money?</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Explore the history and evolution of money from barter to digital currencies.</p>
			</a>
			
			<a href="/bitcoin-tutorial/module/2" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:shadow-gray-900/20 p-6 hover:shadow-lg dark:hover:shadow-gray-900/30 transition-all duration-200 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-600 group">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 group-hover:text-primary-600 dark:group-hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">Module 2: Properties of Good Money</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Evaluate different forms of money based on key properties like durability and scarcity.</p>
			</a>
			
			<a href="/bitcoin-tutorial/module/3" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:shadow-gray-900/20 p-6 hover:shadow-lg dark:hover:shadow-gray-900/30 transition-all duration-200 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-600 group">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 group-hover:text-primary-600 dark:group-hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">Module 3: How Good Money Gets Corrupted</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Understand how and why money gets debased throughout history and the consequences of this corruption.</p>
			</a>
			
			<a href="/bitcoin-tutorial/module/4" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:shadow-gray-900/20 p-6 hover:shadow-lg dark:hover:shadow-gray-900/30 transition-all duration-200 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-600 group">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 group-hover:text-primary-600 dark:group-hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">Module 4: The Proof of Reserves Problem</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Explore the challenges of verifying that claimed monetary reserves actually exist.</p>
			</a>
			
			<a href="/bitcoin-tutorial/module/5" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:shadow-gray-900/20 p-6 hover:shadow-lg dark:hover:shadow-gray-900/30 transition-all duration-200 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-600 group">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 group-hover:text-primary-600 dark:group-hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">Module 5: How Bitcoin Fixes Money</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Discover how Bitcoin was designed to address the fundamental problems of traditional monetary systems.</p>
			</a>
			
			<a href="/bitcoin-tutorial/module/6" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:shadow-gray-900/20 p-6 hover:shadow-lg dark:hover:shadow-gray-900/30 transition-all duration-200 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-600 group">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 group-hover:text-primary-600 dark:group-hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">Module 6: Fiat Economic System Simulation</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Experience the mechanics and incentives of the current fiat monetary system through interactive simulation.</p>
			</a>
			
			<a href="/bitcoin-tutorial/module/7" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:shadow-gray-900/20 p-6 hover:shadow-lg dark:hover:shadow-gray-900/30 transition-all duration-200 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-600 group">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 group-hover:text-primary-600 dark:group-hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">Module 7: Bitcoin Economic System Simulation</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Explore how a Bitcoin-based economy with fixed money supply might function compared to a fiat system.</p>
			</a>
			
			<a href="/bitcoin-tutorial/module/8" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:shadow-gray-900/20 p-6 hover:shadow-lg dark:hover:shadow-gray-900/30 transition-all duration-200 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-600 group">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 group-hover:text-primary-600 dark:group-hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">Module 8: USD vs. BTC - Past 10 Years</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Compare the performance of USD and Bitcoin as stores of value over the past decade.</p>
			</a>
			
			<a href="/bitcoin-tutorial/module/9" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-md dark:shadow-gray-900/20 p-6 hover:shadow-lg dark:hover:shadow-gray-900/30 transition-all duration-200 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-600 group">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 group-hover:text-primary-600 dark:group-hover:text-primary-400 transition-colors">Module 9: Future Projections - Next 10 Years</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Explore different potential futures for Bitcoin adoption over the next decade.</p>
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
